WEBVTT

00:02.336 --> 00:05.806
(upbeat pop song playing)

00:05.839 --> 00:07.808
* See, I just want to dead 'em

00:07.841 --> 00:08.809
* I don't know

00:08.842 --> 00:10.044
* Will I got to Heaven?

00:10.078 --> 00:11.279
* I don't know

00:11.312 --> 00:13.381
(beeping)

00:13.414 --> 00:15.516
* My life ain't perfect

00:15.549 --> 00:18.386
* I can't find the purpose...

00:29.863 --> 00:31.465
Harper!

00:34.168 --> 00:37.105
It's a party,
not a funeral.

00:37.138 --> 00:39.840
Uh, it was my mom's.

00:39.873 --> 00:42.343
God, you can be such
a bitch sometimes.

00:47.415 --> 00:48.382
(earpiece chirps)

00:51.385 --> 00:53.421
*Should I get a reverend?
*I don't know

00:53.454 --> 00:55.623
* Will I go to Heaven?
* I don't know

00:55.656 --> 00:57.791
* See, I just want to dead 'em
* I don't know

00:57.825 --> 01:01.295
* Will I go to Heaven?
* I don't know

01:03.397 --> 01:05.399
* The same, the same,
the same as usual *

01:05.433 --> 01:06.700
* It may just move you

01:06.734 --> 01:10.171
* On stage assume you know I can
choose just to make you move *

01:13.174 --> 01:15.476
* I'm making the news,
you're making a fool *

01:15.509 --> 01:17.678
(earpieces chirping)

01:19.447 --> 01:21.382
* You make me want to flirt

01:21.415 --> 01:23.717
* Make me want to whirl,
see your body on the floor *

01:23.751 --> 01:25.453
* See a trolley on the morgue

01:25.486 --> 01:27.355
* Anybody have a sword to break
this chain off? *

01:27.388 --> 01:28.689
* Somebody please help me take
this brain off *

01:28.722 --> 01:31.225
* I'm feeling like a slave,
this chain of hate *

01:31.259 --> 01:33.227
* It's trained to make
this brain an ape *

01:33.261 --> 01:35.596
* But no cane can take
this pain away *

01:35.629 --> 01:37.665
* So I pray and wait on a rainy
day and say... *

01:37.698 --> 01:39.567
* I just want to dead 'em
* I don't know

